      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but inflamation and low mood are already messing with me so much. i feel like i need the help now rather than waiting for a doctor's appointment which takes forever. if i just took it every other day instead of every day, like maybe 50k every 48 hours, wouldn't that let my body process it better and keep it safe? sounds like a good middle ground to get the benefits without the heavy risk.",
